==宾夕法尼亚州立大学酒店餐饮服务中心==

宾夕法尼亚州立大学酒店餐饮服务中心为宾州州立大学下属企业，向大学的教职员工、在校学生及当地居民提供服务。服务中心向酒店管理学院的在校学生及毕业生提供全职及兼职岗位，给酒店管理学院的学生提供宝贵的实习机会。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abshr.psu.edu/abshr/Resources/Hospitality-Services-Employee-Handbook.cfm#weare |title=Hospitality Services Employee Handbook |publisher=Abshr.psu.edu |date= |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archive-date=2014-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812163057/http://www.abshr.psu.edu/abshr/Resources/Hospitality-Services-Employee-Handbook.cfm#weare |dead-url=no }}</ref> 学院开设的HM380酒店管理课中，学生们将在尼塔尼狮子酒店和宾夕法尼亚州立大学会议中心酒店积累实际操作经验，在前台、客房部、及维修工程部进行为期一学期的轮岗学习。在HM495这门课中，学生将在在职员工的指导下在某一指定部门实习至少一个学期。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bulletins.psu.edu/undergrad/courses/H/HM/495A/201314FA |title=University Bulletin: University Course Descriptions |publisher=Bulletins.psu.edu |date= |accessdate=2014-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812162912/http://bulletins.psu.edu/undergrad/courses/H/HM/495A/201314FA |archive-date=2014-08-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
宾夕法尼亚州立大学酒店餐饮服务中心负责管理运营大学内的尼塔尼狮子酒店、宾夕法尼亚州立大学会议中心酒店、比弗体育场套房、以及盘古拉溜冰场套房。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pshs.psu.edu/ |title=Penn State Hotels - State College Hotels and Conference Center in State College, PA on the Penn State University Campus |publisher=Pshs.psu.edu |date= |accessdate=2014-05-20 |archive-date=2014-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709033941/http://www.pshs.psu.edu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2014年, 尼塔尼狮子酒店被授予AAA四钻酒店，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nittanylioninn.psu.edu/NittanyLionInn/AboutUs.cfm |title=About Us Accommodations |publisher=www.nittanylioninn.psu.edu |date=2013-11-04 |accessdate=2014-08-25 |archive-date=2014-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826160807/http://www.nittanylioninn.psu.edu/NittanyLionInn/AboutUs.cfm |dead-url=no }}</ref>到到网优秀酒店证书<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g53755-d96845-Reviews-Nittany_Lion_Inn-State_College_Pennsylvania.html#REVIEWS |title=Nittany Lion Inn |publisher=www.tripadvisor.com |date=2014 |accessdate=2014-08-25 |archive-date=2014-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723035032/http://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g53755-d96845-Reviews-Nittany_Lion_Inn-State_College_Pennsylvania.html#REVIEWS |dead-url=no }}</ref> 以及美国国家历史保护信托中心的美国历史性酒店证书<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.historichotels.org/hotels-resorts/the-nittany-lion-inn-of-the-pennsylvania-state-university/ |title=The Nittany Lion Inn of the Pennsylvania State University |publisher=www.historichotels.org |date= |accessdate=2014-08-25 |archive-date=2014-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826120006/http://www.historichotels.org/hotels-resorts/the-nittany-lion-inn-of-the-pennsylvania-state-university/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，宾夕法尼亚州立大学会议中心酒店获得了 国际会议中心协会证书。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iacconline.org/penn_stater/index.cfm |title=The Penn Stater Conference Center |publisher=www.iacconline.org |date= |accessdate=2014-08-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826115420/http://www.iacconline.org/penn_stater/index.cfm |archivedate=2014-08-26 }}</ref>

